<h2 id="parting-thoughts">Parting thoughts</h2>

<p>The main takeaway here: there can be multiple valid ways to play any song. Donâ€™t think of these are â€œrightâ€ or â€œwrongâ€ in an absolute sense. Instead, understand that each version offers different opportunities! What worked for the composer (when they wrote the song) may not be a match for you, given equipment or skill level or anything else. Play the version that makes sense depending on your goal, and youâ€™ll be in good shape.</p>
